cz.syntea.xdef.sys

Class BNFGrammar

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.syntea.xdef.sys.BNFGrammar

  • public final class BNFGrammar
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides BNF grammar parsing. BNFGrammar object you can create by the static method compile see:

    compile(BNFGrammar, String, ReportWriter)

    or

    compile(BNFGrammar, File, ReportWriter)

    or

    compile(BNFGrammar, URL, ReportWriter)

    .

    With the created BNFGrammar object you can parse data by method parse(StringParser, String)
